<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Payment Receipt</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .receipt-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .receipt-details table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .receipt-details td {
      padding: 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .receipt-details td:first-child {
      font-weight: bold;
      width: 40%;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Payment Receipt</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for your payment. Your transaction has been processed successfully.</p>
    
    <div class="receipt-details">
      <h2>Payment Details</h2>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>Payment Reference:</td>
          <td>{{paymentId}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Booking Reference:</td>
          <td>{{bookingId}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Payment Amount:</td>
          <td>${{amount}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Payment Method:</td>
          <td>{{paymentMethod}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Payment Date:</td>
          <td>{{paymentDate}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
    
    <p>You can view your payment history and download a copy of this receipt from your account dashboard.</p>
    <a href="#" class="button">View Payment History</a>
    
    <p>If you have any questions about this payment or notice any discrepancies, please contact our customer support team.</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing AutoHub!</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The AutoHub Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 AutoHub. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply directly to this message.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>